    "Context awareness poses challenges due to the intricacies of extensive user data analysis, addressable through AI models offering temporal understanding and adaptability.",
    "Moderate contactless operation challenges exist, particularly for rPPG data collection, and could be reduced by improvements in remote sensing technologies.",
    "Privacy concerns can be managed via robust encryption and user education on data usage.",
    "Noise and environmental condition sensitivity can be tackled with robust noise reduction algorithms and environmental adaptation techniques.",
